cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.DL, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper investigates the structure of linguistic co-occurrence networks in Croatian language. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper analyzes network structure properties. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DL (Deep Learning) are possible categories as the paper uses computational methods to analyze the linguistic networks. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper examines the effects of corpus size and stopword removal on the network structure.
